Package: phyr
Type: Package
Title: Phylogenetic Analysis with R
Version: 0.1.4
Authors@R: c(
    person("Anthony", "Ives", , "arives@wisc.edu", role = c("aut")),
    person("Matthew", "Helmus", , "", role = c("aut")),
    person("Russell", "Dinnage", , "r.dinnage@gmail.com", role = c("aut")),
    person("Daijiang", "Li", , "daijianglee@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: This is a collection of functions to do phylogenetic analysis that were
    wrote by Ives et al. It is easier to update and modify functions in one place than 
    submitting changes to several packages. We rewrote core parts of some functions
    in c++ to speed things up.
